headline.print_headline: Texas Executes Man, 45, for Shooting Spree That Left Two Dead
headline.main: Texas Executes Man, 45, for Shooting Spree That Left Two Dead

lead_paragraph: Texas executed a 45-year-old man on Wednesday for killing two people and wounding two others during a shooting spree sparked by a breakup with his girlfriend.
